---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Hormon Paneli Okuma: AMH, FSH, LH, E2, Prolaktin, TSH | tupbebek.com" description="Kadın ve erkek üreme hormonları, normal değerler ve infertilite ile ilişkisi. AMH, FSH, LH, Estradiol, Prolaktin ve TSH testleri ve yorumlama.">
    <Header />

    <main id="main-content" tabindex="-1" class="pb-24">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <header class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">biotech</span>
                        Klinik Rehber
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl text-on-surface leading-tight mb-8">
                        Hormon Paneli: <span class="text-primary italic">Üreme Hormonları</span> ve Değerlendirme
                    </h1>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-surface-dim">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">verified</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-headline italic text-on-surface text-sm">İnceleme:</p>
                            <p class="font-bold text-primary">Doç. Yayın Kurulu</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:block w-72 shrink-0 aspect-[4/5] bg-surface-container-highest rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                    <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80" src="/images/sorunlar/hormonal-cycles.webp" alt="Hormon paneli" width="512" height="512" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-16">
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body italic mb-12">
                Üreme hormonları infertilite değerlendirmesinin temelini oluşturur. AMH, FSH, LH, Estradiol (E2), Prolaktin ve TSH testleri, over rezervi, ovülasyon fonksiyonu ve endokrin dengesi hakkında kritik bilgi verir. Bu rehber, her hormonun klinik önemini ve referans aralıklarını açıklar.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border-t-2 border-primary-fixed">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-3">bloodtype</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">6+</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-0">Temel üreme hormonu parametresi</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border-t-2 border-primary-fixed">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-3">calendar_today</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">Gün 2–3</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-0">Bazal hormon testleri için ideal gün</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border-t-2 border-primary-fixed">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-3">analytics</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">AMH</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-0">Over rezervinin en güvenilir biyomarkerı</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 1: AMH -->
        <section id="amh" class="bg-surface-container-low py-24 mb-24">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2">
                        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-on-surface mb-6">1. AMH (Anti-Müllerian Hormon)</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant">
                            <p>
                                AMH, over içindeki küçük foliküllerden (antral foliküller) salgılanan bir hormondur ve over rezervinin en güvenilir göstergelerinden biridir. Menstrüel döngünün herhangi bir gününde ölçülebilir—diğer hormonlardan farklı olarak döngü aşamasından etkilenmez.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-primary rounded-xl p-6">
                                <table class="w-full text-sm">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
                                            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-on-surface-variant">AMH Değeri (ng/mL)</th>
                                            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-on-surface-variant">Yorum</th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-red-600">&lt; 1.0</td>
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Düşük over rezervi</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-amber-600">1.0-2.0</td>
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Azalmış rezerv</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-green-700">2.0-4.0</td>
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Normal rezerv</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-amber-600">&gt; 4.0</td>
                                            <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Yüksek (PCOS şüphesi)</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm">
                                AMH düşük çıktığında <a href="/fertilite-koruma" class="text-primary hover:underline">fertilite koruma</a> seçenekleri değerlendirilmelidir. Detaylı bilgi için <a href="/tbbi-sozluk#a" class="text-primary hover:underline">tıbbi sözlük - AMH</a> sayfamıza bakın.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2">
                        <div class="relative group">
                            <img class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full" src="/images/sorunlar/hormonal-cycles.webp" alt="AMH testi" width="512" height="512" loading="lazy"/>
                            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-surface-container-highest p-4 rounded-lg hidden md:block">
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Klinik Veri</p>
                                <p class="text-2xl font-headline">35+</p>
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant">Yaş sonrasında AMH düşüşe geçer</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2: FSH -->
        <section id="fsh" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-24">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-on-surface mb-6">2. FSH (Folikül Stimüle Hormon)</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant">
                        <p>
                            FSH, hipofiz bezinden salgılanan ve overdeki folikül gelişimini uyaran hormondur. Menstrüel döngünün 2. veya 3. gününde ölçülür. Yüksek bazal FSH, over rezervinin azaldığını gösterir.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-primary rounded-xl p-6">
                            <table class="w-full text-sm">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
                                        <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-on-surface-variant">FSH (mIU/mL)</th>
                                        <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-on-surface-variant">Yorum</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                                        <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-green-700">&lt; 8</td>
                                        <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Normal, iyi yanıt</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                                        <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-amber-600">8-12</td>
                                        <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Azalmış rezerv</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-red-600">&gt; 12</td>
                                        <td class="py-2 pr-4 text-on-surface-variant">Düşük over fonksiyonu</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <div class="relative group">
                        <img class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full" src="/images/rehberler/hormone-tracking.webp" alt="FSH takibi" width="512" height="512" loading="lazy"/>
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-surface-container-highest p-4 rounded-lg hidden md:block">
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Klinik Veri</p>
                            <p class="text-2xl font-headline">Gün 2-3</p>
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant">Bazal FSH ölçüm günü</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3: Prolaktin & TSH -->
        <section id="prolaktin" class="bg-surface-container-low py-24 mb-24">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2">
                        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-on-surface mb-6">3. Prolaktin ve TSH</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant">
                            <p>
                                <strong>Prolaktin (PRL)</strong> süt üretiminden sorumlu hormondur. Yüksek prolaktin (hiperprolaktinemi) ovülasyonu baskılayarak infertiliteye yol açar. Normal değer: &lt; 25 ng/mL. Düşük doz bromocriptine veya cabergoline ile tedavi edilebilir.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <strong>Tiroit Stimule Hormon (TSH)</strong> tiroid fonksiyonlarını düzenler. Hem hipotiroid hem de hipertiroid, menstrüel düzensizlik ve infertiliteye neden olabilir. İnfertilite tedavisinde ideal TSH aralığı: 0.5-2.5 mIU/L.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-primary rounded-xl p-6">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-sm mb-3">Prolaktin ve TSH Referans Değerleri</h4>
                                <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                                    <p><strong>Prolaktin:</strong> &lt; 25 ng/mL (kadın)</p>
                                    <p><strong>TSH:</strong> 0.5–2.5 mIU/L (infertilite hedefi)</p>
                                    <p><strong>TSH (genel):</strong> 0.4–4.0 mIU/L</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm">
                                Hormon düzensizliklerinin <a href="/kadin-infertilitesi" class="text-primary hover:underline">kadın infertilitesi</a> üzerindeki etkileri ve <a href="/tani-sureci" class="text-primary hover:underline">tanı süreci</a> hakkında bilgi için ilgili sayfalarımızı ziyaret edin.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2">
                        <div class="relative group">
                            <img class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full" src="/images/sorunlar/hormonal-cycles.webp" alt="Prolaktin ve TSH" width="512" height="512" loading="lazy"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Related Pages -->
        <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-16">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl text-on-surface mb-6">İlgili Sayfalar</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <a href="/tani-sureci" class="border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2">assignment</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-sm">Tanı Süreci</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mt-1">Hormon testleri ve değerlendirme</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/kadin-infertilitesi" class="border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2">woman</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-sm">Kadın İnfertilitesi</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mt-1">Hormonal bozukluklar ve etkileri</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/tbbi-sozluk" class="border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2">menu_book</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-sm">Tıbbi Sözlük</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mt-1">AMH, FSH, LH terim açıklamaları</p>
                </a>
                <a href="/makaleler/laboratuvar-raporu-yorumlama" class="border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2">biotech</span>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface text-sm">Lab Raporu Yorumlama</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant mt-1">Hormon ve semen analizi sonuçları</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Doktor Onay -->
        <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-16">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-primary flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-surface-dim shrink-0">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">verified</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="font-headline text-lg text-on-surface mb-1">Doç. Yayın Kurulu</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
                        Bu içerik, üreme sağlığı alanında uzman <strong class="text-primary">tupbebek.com yayın kurulu</strong> tarafından tıbbi açıdan incelenmiş ve onaylanmıştır.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Yasal Uyarı -->
        <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="bg-amber-50/50 border border-amber-200/50 rounded-xl p-6 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
                <p><strong class="text-on-surface">Yasal Uyarı:</strong> Bu içerik yalnızca bilgilendirme amaçlıdır ve tıbbi tavsiye niteliği taşımaz. Hormon değerleri bireysel olarak yorumlanmalıdır. Sonuçlarınız için bir uzmanla görüşün.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
